description:
QciProfileOperatorDefined: This table stores operator-defined QoS Class Identifier (QCI) profiles for radio access networks.

- dateTime: Timestamp indicating when the data was recorded.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographical area.
- CellId: Unique identifier for the cell.
- Id2: Secondary identifier for the cell (potentially redundant with CellId).
- Id3: Tertiary identifier (mostly 'default' in this sample).
- Id4: QCI profile identifier.
- vsDataType: Data type identifier ('vsDataQciProfileOperatorDefined').
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format ('EricssonSpecificAttributes').
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.serviceType: Type of service associated with the QCI profile.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.pdcpSNLength: Length of the Packet Data Convergence Protocol (PDCP) sequence number.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.pdbOffset: Offset for Packet Delay Budget (PDB).
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dataFwdPerQciEnabled: Indicates whether data forwarding per QCI is enabled.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.endcProfileRef: Reference to the End-to-End Connection (E2E) profile.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.counterActiveMode: Indicates whether counters are active.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dscp: Differentiated Services Code Point (DSCP) value.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.srsAllocationStrategy: Strategy for allocating sounding reference signals (SRS).
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.qci: QoS Class Identifier.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dlMaxWaitingTime: Maximum waiting time for downlink data.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.inactivityTimerOffset: Offset for inactivity timer.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.harqPriority: Hybrid ARQ priority.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.tReorderingDl: Reordering timer for downlink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.measReportConfigParams: Parameters for measurement report configuration.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.priority: Priority level.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.tReorderingUl: Reordering timer for uplink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.laaSupported: Indicates whether Licensed Assisted Access (LAA) is supported.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.aqmMode: Active Queue Management (AQM) mode.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.rlfProfileRef: Reference to the Radio Link Failure (RLF) profile.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dlMaxHARQTxQci: Maximum number of HARQ transmissions for downlink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.rohcForUlDataEnabled: Indicates whether Robust Header Compression (ROHC) is enabled for uplink data.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.userLabel: User-defined label.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.rlcMode: Radio Link Control (RLC) mode.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.rlfPriority: Priority for RLF handling.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.ulMaxHARQTxQci: Maximum number of HARQ transmissions for uplink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dlResourceAllocationStrategy: Resource allocation strategy for downlink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.relativePriority: Relative priority level.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.ulMaxWaitingTime: Maximum waiting time for uplink data.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.schedulingAlgorithm: Scheduling algorithm used.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.absPrioOverride: Absolute priority override setting.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.priorityFraction: Priority fraction.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dlMinBitRate: Minimum bit rate for downlink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.caOffloadingEnabled: Indicates whether Carrier Aggregation (CA) offloading is enabled.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.qciACTuning: QCI AC tuning parameter.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.logicalChannelGroupRef: Reference to the logical channel group.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.drxProfileRef: Reference to the Discontinuous Reception (DRX) profile.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.qciSubscriptionQuanta: QCI subscription quanta.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.rlcSNLength: Length of the RLC sequence number.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.pdb: Packet Delay Budget.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.drxPriority: DRX priority.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.rohcEnabled: Indicates whether ROHC is enabled.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.zzzTemporary1: Reserved for future use.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.zzzTemporary2: Reserved for future use.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.zzzTemporary3: Reserved for future use.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.resourceAllocationStrategy: Resource allocation strategy.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.zzzTemporary4: Reserved for future use.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.ulMinBitRate: Minimum bit rate for uplink.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.zzzTemporary5: Reserved for future use.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.timerPriority: Timer priority.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.dscpArpMap: DSCP ARP mapping.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.lessMaxDelayThreshold: Maximum delay threshold.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.timerProfileRef: Reference to the timer profile.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.bitRateRecommendationEnabled: Indicates whether bit rate recommendation is enabled.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.paPartitionOverride: PA partition override setting.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.qciProfileOperatorDefinedId: Unique identifier for the QCI profile.
- QciProfileOperatorDefined.resourceType: Type of resource ('NON_GBR').
